{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "8c65275d-9f50-4932-9984-34395df66f77",
		"name": "Knowledgebase & Global Context APIs",
		"description": "Complete CRUD operations for Knowledgebase (KB) and Global Context (GC).\n\n## Response Fields\n\nAll KB, GC, and mapping responses include audit trail fields:\n- `created_by`: User ID (UUID)\n- `created_by_username`: Username for display\n- `updated_by`: User ID (UUID)\n- `updated_by_username`: Username for display\n- `created_at`: Timestamp\n- `updated_at`: Timestamp\n\n## Sections\n\n1. **Knowledgebase (KB)**: Account-scoped semantic search (max 10MB, many-to-many agent mappings)\n2. **KB-Agent Mappings**: Map/unmap KBs to agents, list agent KBs\n3. **Global Context (GC)**: Tenant-scoped behavioral rules (max 5MB, whole-file retrieval)\n4. **RAG Migration**: Rename agent_* collections to kb_* using Qdrant aliases (zero downtime)\n5. **RAG Server Direct**: Low-level vector DB operations (testing/debugging)",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
		"_exporter_id": "1799783"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Knowledgebase (KB) - Account-Scoped",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Create KB",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    const response = pm.response.json();",
									"    if (response.data && response.data.id) {",
									"        pm.collectionVariables.set('kb_id', response.data.id);",
									"        console.log('KB ID saved: ' + response.data.id);",
									"    }",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript",
								"packages": {},
								"requests": {}
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							},
							{
								"key": "x-hasura-user-id",
								"value": "{{user_id}}"
							},
							{
								"key": "x-hasura-user-tenant-id",
								"value": "{{tenant_id}}"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"action\": {\n        \"name\": \"ai_create_kb\"\n    },\n    \"input\": {\n        \"request\": {\n            \"account_id\": \"{{account_id}}\",\n            \"knowledgebase\": {\n                \"name\": \"Product_Documentation\",\n                \"description\": \"Complete product documentation for semantic search\",\n                \"data\": \"Product Name: NudgebeeAI\\nDescription: AI-powered cloud optimization platform\\nFeatures: Cost optimization, Performance monitoring, Security compliance\\nBenefits: Reduce cloud costs by 40%, Improve performance, Automated remediation\",\n                \"format\": \"text\",\n                \"file_name\": \"product_docs.txt\"\n            }\n        }\n    },\n    \"session_variables\": {\n        \"x-hasura-user-id\": \"{{user_id}}\",\n        \"x-hasura-user-tenant-id\": \"{{tenant_id}}\",\n        \"x-hasura-role\": \"user\"\n    }\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{llm_server_url}}/v1/knowledgebases",
							"host": [
								"{{llm_server_url}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"v1",
								"knowledgebases"
							]
						},
						"description": "Create a new knowledge base with semantic search enabled"
					},
					"response": []
				},
